[
    {
        "content": "<p>In the case we want padding is always 0, for example a <code>i32</code> flag:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Flag</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">padding</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">AlwaysZero</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"kt\">u8</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">3</span><span class=\"p\">],</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">bool_field</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">bool</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>with the <code>AlwaysZeor&lt;u8&gt;</code>,  a</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">test</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">flag</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Flag</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">bool</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">flag</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">bool_field</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>should not generate the <code>andi</code> instruction: <a href=\"https://godbolt.org/z/vTcfavozj\">https://godbolt.org/z/vTcfavozj</a></p>",
        "id": 570631532,
        "sender_full_name": "Boqun Feng",
        "timestamp": 1769624627
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Of course, llvm needs to have the corresponding concept.</p>",
        "id": 570631632,
        "sender_full_name": "Boqun Feng",
        "timestamp": 1769624657
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>does this work correctly?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"cp\">#[repr(u8)]</span>\n<span class=\"cp\">#[derive(Clone, Copy, PartialEq, Eq)]</span>\n<span class=\"k\">enum</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">AlwaysZero</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">Zero</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"GAS\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nl\">test:</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nf\">slli</span><span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"no\">a0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"no\">a0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">39</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nf\">srli</span><span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"no\">a0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"no\">a0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">63</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nf\">ret</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 570632143,
        "sender_full_name": "Benno Lossin",
        "timestamp": 1769624819
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Good point, let me try</p>",
        "id": 570632212,
