    {
        "content": "<p>Ah, I think I should have added <code>#[repr(C)]</code> on <code>Flag</code> to fix the layout (and reordering the fields to ensure little endian representive), but no, it doesn't seem working: <a href=\"https://godbolt.org/z/c6YsTbvb9\">https://godbolt.org/z/c6YsTbvb9</a></p>",
        "id": 570633478,
        "sender_full_name": "Boqun Feng",
        "timestamp": 1769625244
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>when I remove <code>repr(C)</code>, I get the output from above</p>",
        "id": 570633596,
        "sender_full_name": "Benno Lossin",
        "timestamp": 1769625282
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>if you add <code>repr(C)</code>, you should make <code>bool_field</code> the last of the fields</p>",
        "id": 570633732,
        "sender_full_name": "Benno Lossin",
        "timestamp": 1769625325
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>well I want <code>Flag</code> is <code>1</code> when it's <code>true</code></p>",
