    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"546447\">Benno Lossin</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/288089-General/topic/A.20.60AlwaysZero.60.20type.20for.20padding.3F/near/570634707\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>maybe I'm not understanding what kind of code you want to get generated</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>I want <code>test()</code> to be just a <code>ret</code>.</p>",
