    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"546447\">Benno Lossin</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/288089-General/topic/A.20.60AlwaysZero.60.20type.20for.20padding.3F/near/570635277\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>you could just cast the pointer and have an invariant on the value?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>That's what we previously have, but I think it hurts the readability. You have to read the code to realize there is a bool there.</p>",
        "id": 570635441,
        "sender_full_name": "Boqun Feng",
        "timestamp": 1769625863
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>you can document it right on the field?</p>",
        "id": 570635485,
        "sender_full_name": "Benno Lossin",
        "timestamp": 1769625880
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"546447\">Benno Lossin</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/288089-General/topic/A.20.60AlwaysZero.60.20type.20for.20padding.3F/near/570635485\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>you can document it right on the field?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Wait, I assume you meant we just define</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"cp\">#[repr(i32)]</span>\n<span class=\"cp\">#[...]</span>\n<span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">enum</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Flag</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">Clear</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">Set</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 570635711,
        "sender_full_name": "Boqun Feng",
        "timestamp": 1769625952
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>if so, then there is no field to document.</p>",
        "id": 570635836,
        "sender_full_name": "Boqun Feng",
        "timestamp": 1769625996
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>this is previously what we have: <a href=\"https://lore.kernel.org/rust-for-linux/20260127125300.3656544-2-tomo@aliasing.net/\">https://lore.kernel.org/rust-for-linux/20260127125300.3656544-2-tomo@aliasing.net/</a></p>",
        "id": 570637370,
        "sender_full_name": "Boqun Feng",
        "timestamp": 1769626388
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"546447\">Benno Lossin</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/288089-General/topic/A.20.60AlwaysZero.60.20type.20for.20padding.3F/near/570635277\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>you could just cast the pointer and have an invariant on the value?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Oh, I think I understand what you meant, seems to me your suggestion means that we still have a struct</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"cp\">#[repr(C, align(4)]</span>\n<span class=\"cp\">#[derive(Clone, Copy, PartialEq, Eq)]</span>\n<span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Flag</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">bool_field</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">bool</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">padding</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">u8</span><span class=\"p\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">3</span><span class=\"p\">],</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>and we have another <code>enum</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"cp\">#[repr(i32)]</span>\n<span class=\"cp\">#[derive(Clone, Copy, PartialEq, Eq)]</span>\n<span class=\"k\">enum</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">BooleanFlag</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">Clear</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">Set</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>and we use <code>transmute()</code> in <code>test()</code> (similar as your suggestion to use pointer):</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">test</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">flag</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Flag</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">bool</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">unsafe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">core</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">mem</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">transmute</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">flag</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">};</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">match</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">v</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">BooleanFlag</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Clear</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kc\">false</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">BooleanFlag</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Set</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kc\">true</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 570645775,
        "sender_full_name": "Boqun Feng",
        "timestamp": 1769629203
    },
